INSERT INTO `pages` (`id`, `page_title`, `page_content`, `page_url`) VALUES
(1, 'How it Works', '<p>Tell us the device issue. You will need to submit few device details by selecting&nbsp; from a predefined set of list of issues. Please choose the closest possibilities.</p>\n\n<p>Once the issue is/ are identified, you will get a price estimate quote. If it suits you, please give us&nbsp; a go ahead to repair. We also give a approximate repair time frame.</p>\n\n<p>You could choose to hand it over to us at any of our local stores or have it courier depending at your ease. We will share the approximate repair time.</p>\n\n<p>Once the device is repaired and ready to be used, we inform you to collect it or choose a delivery option. Make payments once you receive device.</p>\n', ''),
(2, 'Repair in Bulk', '<p>Are there too many repairs for your team to handle? Is your tech team reeling under the pressure of backlog for repair? Are you tired of unresponsive &quot;repair insurance&quot; programs? PC Garage provides wholesale and bulk-rate repair services for many dealers and IT companies around the country. In many cases you&#39;d never know as PC Garage stays behind the scenes.</p>\n\n<p>We can fix devices in any number, whether 10, or 10,000.<br />\nWe are the trusted repair shop for many companies. We have the staff and stock always available for your convenience. As more devices you have for repair, we offer you a tailored cost estimate for you based on the type of repairs required and the number of devices.</p>\n\n<p>We offer</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;1. Mail-in or Drop of services</strong><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;You can mail in your devices or drop them off at any of our conveniently located stores.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;2. No hassle payment and volume pricing</strong><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;We are transparent in our dealings and offer you an estimate before we begin repairs. Our average bulk repair cost is as low as x.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;3. Warranty on repairs</strong><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;We cover everything we do with an x month warranty. While drops and subsequent damage are not covered; any problem due to our install is covered 100%. No questions asked.</p>\n', ''),
(3, 'Book a Repair', '<p><strong>How to book a repair</strong><br />\nOur technicians are highly trained and set the industry standard for device repair.We can fix almost all problems on iPhones, iPads, Sony, Google, HTC and Samsung Galaxy devices. Smartphone, tablet or Laptop, you are just 3 simple steps away from a fully repaired device. If you need help understanding what&#39;s wrong with your device, just fill up a simple form, or bring your device to us at any of our stores or you could even mail-in your device.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Mail-in Device</strong><br />\nAll you need to do is fill out the &rsquo;Request a repair&rsquo; form. Print and send it to us along with your device. Once your device arrives at PC Garage, we will assess it and send you a quote for repair.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Walk-in service</strong><br />\nHave no time to book a service or mail your device to us? Just walk-in to any of our conveniently located stores and get your device fixed on the spot from our expert technicians.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Tracking the order</strong><br />\nThanks for dropping off your device in PC Garage for repair. You can use our online tracking tool to check the repair status of the device. You&rsquo;ll need your repair ID to fill out the tracking tool.<br />\n<strong>Repair Tracker</strong></p>\n\n<p>Repair ID*</p>\n\n<p>Last Name*</p>\n\n<p>Don&rsquo;t have a repair ID? <a href="https://pcgarage.uk.com/page/showpage/16">Click here</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Selling your device</strong><br />\nThere is no quicker or better way to sell your old device for cash or trade in for a new model. At PC Garage we offer you the best value for your old device. If going in for a trade-in, we have an excellent range of both, new and refurbished devices.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nYour device&rsquo;s safety and our brand promise</p>\n\n<p>We take pride in our workmanship and provide high-quality repairs to our customers. We are so confident in the quality of our repairs that we include an x month warranty on all repairs.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our aim is to keep our repair prices low and our repair quality high.</strong></p>\n', ''),
(4, 'Wireless Setup', '<p>Wireless setup</p>\n\n<p>Facing problems with your Internet connection? Or did you just purchase a new router and need help to setup a wireless home or office network? PC Garage is always at your service for your entire Internet and wireless network needs.</p>\n\n<p>Common home network problems</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Loose and not properly hooked cables</li>\n	<li>Unable to connect to internet</li>\n	<li>Weak Wi-Fi signal</li>\n	<li>Weak Wi-Fi passwords</li>\n	<li>Cannot see other computers on the network</li>\n	<li>Slow connection</li>\n	<li>Router configuration</li>\n	<li>Network file sharing</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Benefits of our wireless network setup</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Expert router and wireless configuration</li>\n	<li>Home network connectivity improvement</li>\n	<li>Support on home or business wireless setup</li>\n	<li>Expert analysis on home network problems</li>\n	<li>Extensive experience in wireless setup solutions</li>\n	<li>Complete networking tools</li>\n	<li>Secured wireless home/office network</li>\n	<li>Affordable and excellent service</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Do not risk your home network safety and security, call us to book an appointment with our experts to install and setup your network giving you a peace of mind. We can setup a secure wireless network in your home/office so that you can share anything and everything between as many computers as you like. Our service also offers customized solutions that can be tailored to perfectly fit your specific requirements and exact needs at very affordable rates.</p>\n', ''),
(5, 'About Company', '<p>Over the last 10 years, thousands of customers have trusted PC Garage to get their device issues fixed, quickly and efficiently. Our no risk and fixed price solutions are few of the reasons why customers entrust their device repair needs to us. We take pride in our honesty, clarity, and speed.</p>\n\n<p>We repair all mobile phones, tablets, PDAs and other portable devices along with PCs and laptops. Apart from these, one can also find services for software upgrades, data retrieval, phone unlocking, liquid damage, repairs and replacements of screens.</p>\n\n<p>We have established long-term business relationships with all our vendors. This ensures on-time availability of required parts at competitive prices, enabling us to provide you with quick repair service at a price you can&rsquo;t beat. Transparency is our middle name. We use audited workflow systems and strict security protocols, which ensures that your data, privacy, and identity is protected at all times. Our quick turnaround ensures minimum downtime and disruption to your business and personal lifestyle.</p>\n\n<p>The technicians who work on your devices undergo rigorous training. They are particularly knowledgeable in the diagnosis, service, and repair of mobile devices, PCs and laptops and their components, while also keeping abreast of manufacturer service bulletins. They have all the requisite skills to tackle any issue your device may have.</p>\n\n<p>At PC Garage, in the last 10 years, we have repaired 250,000+ devices and still counting. We have brought smiles to our customers&rsquo; faces and take pride in our professional, prompt and always courteous customer service.</p>\n\n<p>Innovative Team established PC Garage on 08th September 2007 when they realized there was a serious lack of fast, reliable device repair services operating in London city. Most device repair companies were spending all their time selling the products instead of also offering the after-sales hardware and software support that is so greatly needed to cope with the ever-changing face of technology.</p>\n', ''),
(6, 'Careers', '<p><strong>Looking for an exciting career?</strong></p>\n\n<p>We are always seeking talented retail and technical professionals to join the PC garbage team. Join us for a happy, healthy and comfortable work environment and get ready to add more to your experience, exposure and expertise. Sounds like you? Get in touch with us today!</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Current openings:-</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Retail Sales Assistant</strong></p>\n\n<p>Duties:<br />\n&middot; Providing advice on electronic items and repairs to help customers<br />\n&middot; Providing after sales support<br />\n&middot; Complete repair booking, updating and closing<br />\n&middot; Retail store operation and inventory management</p>\n\n<p><strong>Location: </strong>London</p>\n\n<p><strong>Repair Technician</strong></p>\n\n<p>To fit in this role, you will need to have a good understanding of our services, a<br />\nstrong interest in electronic items, a willingness to learn. Previous experience in a<br />\nsimilar set up is preferred.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Location: </strong>London</p>\n\n<p>Please mail you c.v: <strong>jobs@pcgarage.uk.com</strong></p>\n', ''),
(7, 'Our Team', '<p>Innovative Team established PC Garage on 08th September 2007 when they realized there was a serious lack of fast, reliable device repair services operating in London city. Most device repair companies were spending all their time selling the products instead of also offering the after-sales hardware and software support that is so greatly needed to cope with the ever-changing face of technology.</p>\n', ''),
(8, 'Corporate accounts', '<p><strong>Corporate Accounts</strong></p>\n\n<p>For your regular device repair needs we would be happy to onboard you as a corporate member. We offer special prices that better suit the needs of organizations that need more than one device repaired. You also get the flexibility of creating a customized repair plan for your business. Our services are significantly less expensive than repair-insurance and our quality and turnaround time are faster too.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Some of the features of our corporate service are:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Dedicated Corporate Account Manager</li>\n	<li>Credit facilities (subject to status)</li>\n	<li>Fast track ( same day repair) service available</li>\n	<li>Web based tracking and management system with automatic email updates</li>\n	<li>Average repair time of x hours (almost half of most of our competitors)</li>\n	<li>Over 3,000 of the most commonly used parts kept in stock</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Why choose us?</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Low cost, quick repairs</li>\n	<li>Fast Track repair service available</li>\n	<li>Highest Quality OEM parts used</li>\n	<li>Fully trained UK based service technicians</li>\n	<li>Over 150,000 happy customers</li>\n	<li>Prices Include Parts, Labour, Vat and Warranty</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Safety of your data</strong></p>\n\n<p>Privacy and confidentiality of data are extremely important factors for us. We perform a full backup of your device to insure no data is lost when we complete your repair. However, you need not have any fear of personal information being compromised or stolen.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', ''),
(15, 'Why PC Garage', '<p>We understand that your device is an important and crucial part of your life, and we want to make device issues less stressful, time-consuming, and disruptive. At PC Garage,you can expect the best, in both quality and service. So, each time you think device repair, think PC Garage.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Warranty for ALL items serviced</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>We guarantee that you will not discover any defects in the parts replaced or workmanship within this 180-days period.</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Same day express service on most items</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>&nbsp;You simply walkin for repair and walk out with a working device.We provide immediate, expert repair and care for all your mobile devices, so you can stay connected to the things that matter most to you.*</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Full online service tracking and job history</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>Our comprehensive database captures your profile and every repair,we have ever done for you over 10 years.</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Courier service and mail in service available</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>If for some reason you cannot bring your damaged device to our store, you can courier or mail it to us. We shall be happy to take a look at it and advise you on further action.</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>High-level customer referrals with proven high customer satisfaction</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>Our repeat and referral customer traffic has been on a steady increase over the years. This for sure is an indicator of a great customer service and support. This year (2017) we are tracking almost 72% repeats and referrals!</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Competitive pricing</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We are almost as much as 25% cheaper than manufacturer extended warranties. Customers from all over the UK send us their devices for repair.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Trained technicians</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>We offer expert repair solutions through trained and certified technicians.Our fast repair service turnaround ensures minimum downtime and disruption.</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Huge accessories inventory</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>Our long-standing relationships with major component and accessories distributors ensure an almost always-available supply of high-quality accessories and parts.</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Buy refurbished devices</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>Examined by our trained service technicians, these devices are repaired with premium quality parts,reset to their original settings, and rigorously tested through an extensive quality inspection to ensure that they meet our standards for certification as a like-new device.</em></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', ''),
(16, 'FAQs', '<p><strong>Is there anything I should do before sending or handing over my device?</strong></p>\n\n<p>All you need to do is tell us about the issue you&rsquo;re facing, and we shall take care of it.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>What is the guarantee of my device safety?</strong></p>\n\n<p>All of our technicians are well-trained and certified experts. No harm will come to your device.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>How can I track my repair order?</strong></p>\n\n<p>You can use our online tracking tool to check the repair status of the device. You&rsquo;ll need your repair ID to fill out the tracking tool.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Does your price include taxes?</strong></p>\n\n<p>All the prices include the applicable taxes.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>I have lost my repair ID? How do I get it to track my order?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Please write to us at repair@pcgarage.uk.com using the email id you used to register with us, and we shall send you your device repair id.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>What does your No Fix No Fee policy mean?</strong></p>\n\n<p>It represents our customer commitment.You only pay after you test your repaired device and confirming your satisfaction with our work.*</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Can I cancel my repair order?</strong></p>\n\n<p>We repair most devices in less than an hour after we receive your approval on the estimate. Therefore, it is extremely important that you let us know of any change in plans within ( pls mention time frame)of placing your repair order.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Where is your warranty applicable and where not?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Our 180 days warranty is designed to give you a peace of mind after getting your device repaired by us.Your satisfaction is our priority! However, we do not offer any warranty for accidental damage like cracked screen and water damage etc.The warranty that we offer on our services is voided if your device is ever repaired elsewhere after our repair work.</p>\n\n<p>To see our full warranty policy, please follow this link.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>What payment methods do you accept?</strong></p>\n\n<p>We accept Cash,Credit/Debit Card or PayPal (On-Line Payment). We do not accept any personal cheques. Business cheques are only accepted for corporate/bulk accounts.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>I am not a UK resident. How do I pay?</strong></p>\n\n<p>You can make an online payment from anywhere in the world.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Can I see your service reviews somewhere?</strong></p>\n\n<p>You can check the reviews on our website. Also, we invite you to be a part of our Facebook family so that you are up to date about the latest happenings at PC Garage.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Do you offer a wholesale service?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Yes, we do. For corporate and bulk accounts please write to us at &ldquo;businessaccounts@pcgarage.uk.com&rdquo;<a name="_GoBack"></a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>I am not satisfied with your work. What do I do?</strong></p>\n\n<p>We want our customers to be completely&nbsp;satisfied&nbsp;with our services. If you&#39;re not happy with the repairs, we will work with you till we get it right. Please be careful as refunds are not normally provided where you have simply changed your mind, or found the repairs cheaper elsewhere.</p>\n', ''),
(17, 'Terms and Conditions', '<p>Our repair services and products come with certain guarantees that are based on and governed by the laws of England and Wales and shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English Courts.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Service Terms</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. When entering a repair/service contract with PC Garage, whether verbal or written, you agree and understand all prior information provided to you about PC Garage and its services. You also agree to all of the sections of the following Terms and Conditions. As the consumer you acknowledge that you have made all efforts possible to seek and understand important information that relates to you and your selected service. Ultimately, it is your responsibility to understand all terms of services and the associated conditions of repair/warranty before entering a service contract.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2. By providing your device for repair/servicing under our terms and conditions you agree and accept that you have either (A) you have made a backup copy of your data and removed any confidential, proprietary or personal information or (B) You have assumed the risk that such information or media may be lost, corrupted or compromised during our repair or service. You further acknowledge and agree that PC Garage cannot guarantee the safety, security or integrity of any data that remains on your product while it is undergoing service or repair.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3. PC Garage is not responsible for events that are out of PC Garage reasonable control which lead to failures to complete a service, whether delayed or incomplete. PC Garage will not be held liable under these circumstances.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Modifications to Service Terms</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. Considering these Terms and Conditions, PC Garage will provide repair services of your product for the charges quoted by the PC Garage team unless further faults with the device are discovered by our tecnicians at the time of repair.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2. Further problems with your device may mean that the previously stated quote is now deemed not contractible, and for this reason we ask you to provide us with all important information about the condition and past conditions of your device so we can best assist you as the customer. It is likely that other costs will be incurred in repairing the device to restore the device to a fully working order, if further faults are found. However, the pre-existing contract terms should not change. If they are likely to change due to newly found device conditions, you are entitled to be informed about this by PC Garage.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3. If the requested services require a modification to the pre-existing contract not originally known to PC Garage, PC Garage will seek your approval of the revised estimated repair cost, and you will not be billed unfairly for any price fluctuations which have not been agreed upon previously. If you wish to not go ahead with the extra cost deemed necessary to repair your device further, you may be asked to pay a diagnostic fee, unless the service was contracted with a &lsquo;no diagnosis fees&rsquo; agreement.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;4. PC Garage also reserves the right to refuse service if a team member decides your device is not as described upon establishment of the repair contract. The customer may be accountable for a diagnostic fee in this and similar circumstances.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Warranty Terms and Conditions</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. When the product is covered by an PC Garage warranty, PC Garage will perform repairs only covered under the terms of that warranty.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2. If your product is repaired by PC Garage outside of a warranty claim, PC Garage warrants that (a) All repairs will be performed in a competent and professional manner and (b) all parts used to repair your device will be free from defects in materials and workmanship for a period of ninety (90) calendar days. If either of these points are not met, you are entitled to claim our 90 Day Warranty.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3. Our 90 Day Warranty is valid from the time of repair upon<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;transaction completion, but not settlement, for the period of<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;90 (ninety) complete calendar days.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;4. Our 90 Day Warranty covers the replacement of replaced parts which have failed under manufacturer defects and fair wear and tear. Fair wear and tear does not include customer abuse and PC Garage holds the right as repairer to determine which cases fall under &lsquo;fair wear and tear&rsquo;, &lsquo;manufacturer defects and &lsquo;customer abuse&rsquo;.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5. Repair payments cannot be refunded if the device can be repaired under the original service contract.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;6. If the original service contract cannot be met under a warranty claim, the payment value will be refunded inclusive of any tax paid.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;7. Warranties for all other hardware/software sold through PC Garage carries the original manufacturer warranty, if this can be provided by the manufacturer.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;8. If your device is repaired under warranty, the faulty replaced part becomes the property of PC Garage</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;9. Replacement parts, and warranty claims carry an explicit 90 days Warranty on their failure as denoted in Section 3 &ndash; 2 &ndash;(b)</p>\n\n<p><strong>Payment Terms</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. Unless your product is repaired under warranty without charge, you will pay PC Garage the amount shown on your given invoice. You agree that you will pay for all services you agree to, and that PC Garage may charge your payment method for any products purchased and for any additional amounts (including any taxes and late fees, as applicable) that may be accrued by or in connection with your Account. YOU ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR THE TIMELY PAYMENT OF ALL FEES AND FOR PROVIDING PC GARAGE WITH A VALID PAYMENT METHOD FOR PAYMENT OF ALL FEES.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2. Your payment is due once the contracted repair/service has been completed, and in the case of repairs your device has been returned to you. Both parties must agree that the service contract has been met in full. If one party decides the contracted service has not been completed, payment should not be made. It is then PC Garage responsibility to complete the service contract, and the customer to make payment. If the service contract cannot be met and PC Garage cancels the service contract before payment is received, there is no fee to the customer.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Loss/Damage of</strong><strong> Devices</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. If any product should be damaged or lost whilst in PC Garage custody, PC Garage liability will be limited to the current second hand value of that device. The device&rsquo;s worth will be decided by PC Garage, taking into account for certain factors such as the aesthetic and functional condition of the device as a whole and also individually through its parts/components.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2. To the extent permitted by law PC Garage cannot be found liable for any of the devices data loss, consequential damages, indirect, exemplary and loss of profits (as outlined in our Privacy Policy). Also to the extent permitted by law PC Garage has no liability for the loss or damage of software applications and/or data.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3. The repair of your goods may result in the loss of data. PCGarage is not liable for any loss of software, data stored, residing or recorded in your product. Including removable data, confidential personal or proprietary information. By providing your product under our terms and conditions you agree and accept that you have either (A) you have made a backup copy of your data and removed any confidential,proprietary or personal information or (B) You have assumed the risk that such information or media may be lost, corrupted or compromised during our repair or service. You further acknowledge and agree that PC Garage cannot guarantee the safety, security or integrity of any data that remains on your product while it is undergoing service or repair.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Unclaimed Goods</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. It is a condition of PC Garage that any product repaired is subject to the disposal of uncollected goods legislation. This legislation allows PC Garage the right of sale exercisable in certain circumstances. If your product remains unclaimed, PCGarage reserves the right under law to dispose of that product in whichever way PC Garage deems fit. This includes the sale of your device with no fiscal compensation to the original owner.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Required Software Installation</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. If the repair service involves transferring information or installing software, you agree that any PC Garage team member has the need to copy the required information and agree to the terms of the software being installed in order to complete the agreed service contract. You hereby authorize PC Garage to transfer information and install required software and accept such terms on your behalf in performing the service.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Changes to the Terms and Conditions</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. PC Garage holds the right to change the above Terms and Conditions at any time, and it your responsibility to check you have read the most recent revision.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2. All service contracts will be completed under the Terms and Conditions that governed the contract establishment.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3. Any revision to the Document only affect future service contracts.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;4. These Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of England and Wales and shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English Courts.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5. These Terms and Conditions are the only ones that govern PC Garage&rsquo;s product or services. Except otherwise stated by these terms and conditions or by a PC Garage team member, no other oral or written terms or conditions apply.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;6. No one has the authority from PC Garage to change any of these Terms and Conditions without authorization by management.</p>\n', ''),
(18, 'Data Recovery', '<p>When is a data&nbsp;recovery&nbsp;service required?</p>\n\n<p>A data recovery service is required when:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Your storage device media is physically damaged&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Your data is on a mobile device&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>You&rsquo;re not comfortable doing it o your own using step-by-step software&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Recovering your data is important and for that you need experts</p>\n\n<p>A data recovery expert can help you:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Bring back lost files or information</li>\n	<li>Saving hours of frustration</li>\n	<li>Recovering data you might never have seen again</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Things you can try yourself first&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><em>Rebooting is the &lsquo;Golden Rule&rsquo; for a reason</em></strong></p>\n\n<p>Reboot your computer, your printer, your router, your mobile phone, your USB hub and everything else you&rsquo;re having a problem with. By reboot, we mean turn it off, wait a good minute or two, and turn it back on.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><em>Reinstall and update your applications</em></strong></p>\n\n<p>Uninstalling and reinstalling an application would clear out any corrupt data or broken settings. It would also ensure that you&rsquo;re running the latest version of the software, complete with the latest compatibility updates and bug fixes.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><em>Check for spyware and malware</em></strong></p>\n\n<p>Update your antivirus and antispyware software to the latest versions and run the most comprehensive scans.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><em>Reinstall your operating system</em></strong></p>\n\n<p>Do a factory reset for your phone. Once you reinstall your OS your computer will go back to being as it was when you first bought it. That means broken files, corrupt data, dodgy extensions and any viruses will be wiped away. So will all your documents, photos, emails, apps and settings, so please ensure you have everything safely backed up.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>What you should expect&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>When the above steps don&rsquo;t work, we&rsquo;re here to help.<a name="_GoBack"></a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A &lsquo;Certified Technician Only&rsquo; will fix your phone</strong></p>\n\n<p>Our technicians are trained and have many years of hands-onexperience of repairing mobile phones and other devices.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Repair vs New</strong></p>\n\n<p>We will always do what we can to fix your device so you don&rsquo;t have to buy a new one &mdash; and 9 times out of 10, repairing your device will be cheaper than replacing it.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Bringing it to us won&rsquo;t void the warranty</strong></p>\n\n<p>Any accidental damage to your phone and phew! the phone&rsquo;s limited one-year warranty is already voided. Coming to PC Garage won&rsquo;t void your warranty. According to a memo sent to Apple retail employees, customers getting their device&rsquo;s screen repaired by a third-party source no longer void their warranty like it once did</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Safety of your data</strong></p>\n\n<p>Privacy and confidentiality of data are extremely important factors for us. We perform a full backup of your device to insure no data is lost when we complete your repair. However, you need not have any fear of personal information being compromised or stolen.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>What&#39;s Possible and what not</p>\n\n<p>We are dedicated to resolving your device woes. Our certified and friendly staff will repair your broken,faulty or damaged device to your satisfaction. Also, if you are interested you can trade off your old device for a new or a new-like refurbished phone. Most of our repairs are completed the same day. We shall notify you when the device is un-repairable and the reasond for it.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Disclaimer</strong></p>\n\n<p>This disclaimer covers all devices that come for repair to PC Garage.</p>\n\n<p>While undertaking the repair process, we will use all our expertise, diligent work and care to bring your device back to working the way it was. However, you at times might be able to observe slight variation of the device before and after it had been worked on. This is unavoidable. Our professional technicians will do their very best to make sure all devices worked upon will stay close to the original shape and design Also,Please take note of your device&rsquo;s pre existing condition before submitting it for repair work. We are only responsible for the part we replace.</p>\n\n<p>By submitting your device for repair hereafter, you agree that you not hold PC Garage or any of its technician and staff on this matter.</p>\n', ''),
(19, 'Sell Your Device in minutes', '<p>Have you recently upgraded your device? Or do you have an old one or two just sitting around retired?</p>\n\n<p>We may be interested in buying your unwanted device subject to a few conditions.</p>\n', '');
